Class Swf.Import

java.lang.Object
  org.as2lib.ant.Swf.Import
Enclosing class:
Swf
public static class Swf.Import
extends java.lang.Object

Import represents a shared library import. The specified swf is imported as library.

This task can take the following arguments:

  • file
  • url
  • include

Author:
Simon Wacker
